1
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:04,120
As long as it saves my son's life,

2
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,200
I'm willing to do anything.

3
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,479
Very well.

4
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,919
Then I want you

5
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:14,319
to bring me the Primordial Violet Qi Art.

6
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:21,599
The Primordial Violet Qi Art is our sect's core technique.

7
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:25,159
Only the Mystic Medicine Association's Medicine Venerable and Medicine Prodigy can access it.

8
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:27,039
I have no way to get near it!

9
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:29,719
That's your problem.

10
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:33,680
But your son's illness, well,

11
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:38,319
I'm afraid there's no time for you to hesitate.

12
00:02:46,919 --> 00:02:50,599
Any other manual, I can find a way,

13
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:52,400
but the Primordial Violet Qi Art, I really...

14
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,960
You see this?

15
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:11,120
This is what the copy of

16
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:15,280
your half-fragmented Primordial Violet Qi Art

17
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:18,479
has reduced me to today.

18
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,800
To undo this,

19
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:27,400
I must obtain the complete text.

20
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,439
So,

21
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:38,800
I want only the Primordial Violet Qi Art.

22
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,280
It's still there.

23
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,520
It's still there.

24
00:04:25,839 --> 00:04:27,240
What's going on here?

25
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,600
You said you could cure him!

26
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:35,639
I told you before,

27
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:38,040
your son's illness,

28
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:41,839
I'm only suppressing it, not curing it.

29
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:45,759
But saving his life

30
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:47,600
isn't actually difficult.

31
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,399
However,

32
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:52,279
you must

33
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:55,920
deliver the Primordial Violet Qi Art to me first.

34
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,360
Don't worry.

35
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:05,399
I've already used Vile Qi

36
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:07,920
to stabilize his Heart Meridian.

37
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:12,959
From now on, just give him the medicine on schedule,

38
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:19,920
and it'll keep the Vile Qi balanced with

39
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:22,839
the Yin and Yang Qi inside his body,

40
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:27,000
thus prolonging his life.

41
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,879
What is this medicine made of?

42
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:32,319
Good question.

43
00:05:34,279 --> 00:05:39,439
Naturally, they're all rather unusual ingredients.

44
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:41,759
Psoralea,

45
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:43,199
black snake,

46
00:05:43,199 --> 00:05:46,319
black ginseng, musk blood,

47
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,439
and human blood.

48
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,040
What's more,

49
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:53,120
only from a child under five,

50
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:58,399
a living source works best.

51
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:04,959
You...

52
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:08,439
Why are you looking at me like that?

53
00:06:13,199 --> 00:06:15,639
Think it's filthy?

54
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,959
Don't forget,

55
00:06:20,439 --> 00:06:26,279
you were the one kneeling here, begging me to treat him.

56
00:06:34,319 --> 00:06:35,279
Besides,

57
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:38,680
Apothecary Li,

58
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:43,439
how did you climb up from being

59
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:47,120
the weakest Heaven-rank Disciple of your generation

60
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:50,279
in the Mystic Medicine Association to where you are today?

61
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,839
Could it be

62
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:58,519
that you relied on medical skill alone?

63
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,959
You lied to me.

64
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:23,160
Just keep doing as I say,

65
00:07:25,199 --> 00:07:30,360
and I'll deliver the medicine to your son on time each month.

66
00:07:33,839 --> 00:07:34,639
But...

67
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:38,639
if I ever sense

68
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:41,160
that you're being disloyal,

69
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:45,879
I guarantee your son

70
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:49,199
won't live another month.

71
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,519
Don't worry.

72
00:07:57,639 --> 00:08:01,920
This is just insurance.

73
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:04,360
As long as

74
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:11,519
you obediently bring me the Primordial Violet Qi Art,

75
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,120
none of this

76
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,199
will be a problem.

77
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:44,519
Mouren,

78
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:45,720
You...

79
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,639
What are you doing?

80
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,240
The Medicine King Ceremony is tomorrow.

81
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,039
I came to check the herb inventory.

82
00:09:02,759 --> 00:09:03,360
Give it to me.

83
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,960
This is

84
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,679
Vile Qi corrosion.

85
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,879
No...

86
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:37,559
You swapped the medicinal herbs?

87
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:40,840
Do you know how many patients depend on these?

88
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,200
What do you know?

89
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:48,320
Xiang'er's life hangs by a thread.

90
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,440
I only took some medicinal herbs

91
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,360
to trade with He Quan's side.

92
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,840
I had no choice.

93
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,759
You did have a choice.

94
00:09:57,399 --> 00:10:00,399
You chose to harm others for your own child.

95
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:09,080
Would you just stand by and watch your son

96
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,840
die right before your eyes?

97
00:10:11,279 --> 00:10:13,200
I would never trade other people's lives

98
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:16,200
for my son's life.

99
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,480
Mouren.

100
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,440
For this matter,

101
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:26,000
you'll answer to the Kunyuan Council yourself.

102
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:44,360
If this ever gets exposed,

103
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,600
you,

104
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,679
your son,

105
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:50,279
and your entire Li family will be finished.

106
00:10:52,519 --> 00:10:53,440
I understand.

107
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,919
I'll clean it up.

108
00:11:23,279 --> 00:11:24,200
Stay back!

109
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:24,960
Who are you?

110
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,840
Don't come any closer!

111
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,840
Don't touch me!

112
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:27,879
Let go!

113
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:31,120
You're the one who killed us!

114
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:32,720
It wasn't me!

115
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,799
You are the murderer!

116
00:11:33,799 --> 00:11:34,679
It's all your fault!

117
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:35,720
Give us back our lives!

118
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,879
It was you!

119
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:37,799
It was you!

120
00:11:37,799 --> 00:11:38,200
It was you!

121
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,200
Stay away from me!

122
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:40,080
It wasn't me!

123
00:11:40,879 --> 00:11:41,440
It wasn't me!

124
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:44,080
It wasn't me! Stay back!

125
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,200
Don't come near me!

126
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:51,080
Stay back!

127
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:04,679
Xiang'er!

128
00:12:14,919 --> 00:12:17,320
Xiang'er!

129
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,840
My son!

130
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,320
I was wrong.

131
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,240
It's all my fault, son.

132
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,399
Are you okay?

133
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,480
What are you doing?

134
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:25,879
Get away!

135
00:12:25,879 --> 00:12:26,879
Let me try.

136
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:27,720
I can save him.

137
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:29,720
Why?

138
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:32,559
Someone else will judge his right and wrong.

139
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,200
I am a healer.

140
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,759
I only deal with my patient's life and death.

141
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,919
Your Violet Qi is depleted.

142
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,200
Let's see what tricks you have left.

143
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:12,759
Guards! Kill him!

144
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:26,440
Medicine Venerable.

145
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,600
Perfect.

146
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,799
You came just in time.

147
00:13:43,639 --> 00:13:44,480
Master.

148
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,159
You're not dead!

149
00:13:48,759 --> 00:13:50,519
Are you cursing your master?

150
00:13:50,519 --> 00:13:53,320
Your master is blessed with great fortune.

151
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:54,320
I won't be dying anytime soon.

152
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,080
You old man, always bragging.

153
00:14:19,279 --> 00:14:20,440
Just look at you.

154
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,279
You're really useless.

155
00:14:22,279 --> 00:14:23,720
Your Violet Qi is fully mastered,

156
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:24,919
and you...

157
00:14:24,919 --> 00:14:26,840
Look what these three guys

158
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,159
have done to you.

159
00:14:28,159 --> 00:14:29,840
You've really disgraced your master.

160
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:33,360
I just hadn't had a chance to strike yet.

161
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,799
If you'd come a little later,

162
00:14:34,799 --> 00:14:36,120
I'd have taken them all down, guaranteed.

163
00:14:37,039 --> 00:14:38,080
Brag away.

164
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,919
You make it sound so convincing.

165
00:14:39,919 --> 00:14:40,639
If I hadn't shown up,

166
00:14:40,639 --> 00:14:41,759
would you even be standing here?

167
00:15:00,759 --> 00:15:02,720
The Venerable Healer Token is here.

168
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,720
The Venerable Healer Token.

169
00:15:13,039 --> 00:15:16,279
Yang Yunfan, having achieved Breakthrough and Heart Inquiry

170
00:15:17,159 --> 00:15:18,919
and Primordial Violet Reunification,

171
00:15:20,279 --> 00:15:23,159
is officially appointed as Medicine Prodigy.

172
00:15:25,039 --> 00:15:27,840
Greetings, Lord Medicine Prodigy.

173
00:15:39,679 --> 00:15:40,679
Hurry, take it.

174
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:46,960
Master,

175
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:50,639
Isn't this display a bit too grand?

176
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:55,879
If your master doesn't put on a show,

177
00:15:55,879 --> 00:15:57,120
then later,

178
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:59,159
who'd remember me?

179
00:15:59,159 --> 00:16:00,960
Then when can I wear robes like yours?

180
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,480
What's the rush? So many people around.

181
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:05,080
Let's go.

182
00:16:28,279 --> 00:16:29,759
President Ye, here's the new batch of medicine.

183
00:16:29,759 --> 00:16:31,039
Please take a look.

184
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:37,039
President Ye.

185
00:16:37,039 --> 00:16:38,000
Save me.

186
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,159
I really can't take it anymore.

187
00:16:39,159 --> 00:16:40,320
Please give me less work.

188
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:42,360
It's been over 300 cases this morning alone.

189
00:16:43,039 --> 00:16:44,159
There are way too many people.

190
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:46,840
There's nothing we can do.

191
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:49,080
Red Fire Hall and Mystic Water Hall are all locked up.

192
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:51,000
The Mystic Medicine Association is short on hands.

193
00:16:51,519 --> 00:16:54,279
Besides, you're way too famous right now.

194
00:16:54,279 --> 00:16:55,679
All of Qijiang City

195
00:16:55,679 --> 00:16:57,519
wants the legendary Medicine Prodigy

196
00:16:57,519 --> 00:16:58,759
to treat them personally.

197
00:16:58,759 --> 00:16:59,639
Just hang in there.

198
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:01,480
Then what about this?

199
00:17:03,559 --> 00:17:04,480
What's this supposed to mean?

200
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:07,160
You said you'd keep these photos for yourself.

201
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:08,440
How did they become flyers?

202
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,279
Is this normal?

203
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:10,920
We already took them,

204
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:11,960
and the money's already spent.

205
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,200
Gotta make use of the resources.

206
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:14,559
Keep it up!

207
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,759
I'm no Medicine Prodigy.

208
00:17:19,759 --> 00:17:21,000
I'm a medicine slave!

209
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:24,000
I quit!
